  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à Kdebase-Runtime</title>

    <para>kdebase-runtime is for runtime dependencies et is a required 
    package for <application>KDE</application> applications like kdesu, 
    kfile etc.</para>

    &lfs67_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Information sur le paquet</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>Téléchargement (HTTP)&nbsp;: <ulink url="&kde4baseruntime-download-http;"/></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Téléchargement (FTP)&nbsp;: <ulink url="&kde4baseruntime-download-ftp;"/></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Somme de contrôle MD5 du téléchargement&nbsp;: &kde4baseruntime-md5sum;</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
